sin city : a dame to kill for ( also known as frank miller 's sin city : a dame to kill for ) is a 2014 american neo-noir action crime film and follow-up to the 2005 film sin city . directed by robert rodriguez and frank miller , the script is written by miller and is primarily based on the second book in the sin city series by miller . one of the smaller plots of the film is based on the short story " just another saturday night , " which is collected in booze , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , & bullets , the sixth book in the comic series . two original stories ( " the long bad night " and " nancy 's last dance " ) were created exclusively for the film written by miller . the film stars an ensemble cast including returning cast members mickey rourke , jessica alba , rosario dawson , jaime king , powers boothe and bruce willis . newcomers to the series include josh brolin , joseph gordon-levitt , eva green , dennis haysbert , ray liotta , christopher lloyd , jamie chung , jeremy piven , christopher meloni , stacy keach , lady gaga , alexa vega , julia garner , and juno temple . the film was released on august 22 , 2014 on 2d , 3d and reald 3d . unlike the first film , a dame to kill for was a commercial failure , grossing $ 39 million against production budget of $ 65 million . it received mixed reviews from film critics .